ee.guardtime.proov.tlv

Class DatafileStructure

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guardtime.ksi.tlv.TLVStructure
      • ee.guardtime.proov.tlv.DatafileStructure

  • public class DatafileStructure
extends com.guardtime.ksi.tlv.TLVStructure
    This class is for storing metadata about data files. We use TLV format here. Metadata contain following information: datafile URI, datafile Hash and Hashing algorithm
